.idea-to-production
  .container
    %h1 Move faster from idea to production.

    .row.tools-row
      .col-xs-12.col-sm-6
        %h3 Your tools make all the difference.
        .description
          GitLab includes Git repository management, issue tracking, code review,
          an IDE, activity streams, wikis, and more.
      .col-xs-12.col-sm-6.image-column
        = image_tag "/images/home/value-illustration-1.png", alt: "Tools"

    .row.tools-row
      .col-xs-12.col-sm-6.col-sm-push-6
        %h3 Shorten feedback cycles and raise confidence in your code.
        .description
          GitLab has built-in CI and CD to test, build, and deploy your code.
          You can easily monitor the progress of your tests and build pipeliens.
          Then deploy with the confidence that your code has been tested across
          multiple environments.
      .col-xs-12.col-sm-6.col-sm-pull-6.image-column
        = image_tag "/images/home/value-illustration-2.png", alt: "Tools"

    .row.tools-row
      .col-xs-12.col-sm-6
        %h3 Cover your bases by adding control to your development process.
        .description
          With LDAP group sync, git hooks, automated testing, and audit trails,
          GitLab Enterprise Edition gives admin user management capabilities
          without imposing on developers' workflows.
      .col-xs-12.col-sm-6.image-column
        = image_tag "/images/home/value-illustration-3.png", alt: "Tools"

    .row.tools-row
      .col-xs-12.col-sm-6.col-sm-push-6
        %h3 Focus on building your product, not configuring your tools.
        .description
          Tools should be simple, intuitive, and just work out of the box.
          GitLab comes in deb or rpm file. It installs in minutes, has a
          friendly UI, and offers detailed documentation on every feature.
      .col-xs-12.col-sm-6.col-sm-pull-6.image-column
        = image_tag "/images/home/value-illustration-4.png", alt: "Tools", class: "building-img"
